modelVersions.description:
A lora based on a very skillful artist (dduck kong)

  • Works best at 0.8-1.0 strength

  • Use clip skip 2

  • Easynegative embedding

  • model used orange

Training settings

92images

10 repeats

4 batchsize

6 epochs

1e-4 learning rate

1e-4 text_encoder

1e-3 unet_lr

512res

128 dim

128network_alpha
